      "text": "说道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "众人鼓掌叫好，都说：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊哟",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那头陀正没好气，又重重一掌拍在桌上，猛喝：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那汉子道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那头陀喝道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我去管管。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青青正想瞧两人打架，不料那汉子好似怕了头陀的威势，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那瘦小汉子却高声叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青青悄声说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样子真难看，那又是什么武功了？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_tian_guang",
      "speaker_name": "沙天广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "程青竹道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_tian_guang",
      "speaker_name": "沙天广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沙天广道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正要上前拆解，袁承志笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊哟，不好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那头陀道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那汉子道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_gui_nan",
      "speaker_name": "胡桂南",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "胡桂南见他知道自己姓名和外号，很是欢喜，忙道：",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qing_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "程青竹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又见到倚在桌边的一根青竹，知道青竹帮中的人所持青竹以竹节多少分位份高下，这枝青竹竟有十三节，那是帮中最高的首领，便向程青竹作揖，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qing_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "程青竹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "程青竹呵呵笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_gui_nan",
      "speaker_name": "胡桂南",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁罗汉笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_gui_nan",
      "speaker_name": "胡桂南",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "胡桂南笑道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_gui_nan",
      "speaker_name": "胡桂南",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁罗汉一拍桌子，叫道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qing_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "程青竹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "众人又是一阵大笑。程青竹笑道：",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_gui_nan",
      "speaker_name": "胡桂南",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "胡桂南笑道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_gui_nan",
      "speaker_name": "胡桂南",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁罗汉奇道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_gui_nan",
      "speaker_name": "胡桂南",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "胡桂南道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁罗汉道：",
